}}《{{lang|en|'''Greatest Hits'''}}》是英国摇滚乐队[[皇后乐队|皇后乐队]]的首张[[精选辑|精选辑]]，于1981年10月26日在英国发行<ref>{{cite journal |title=Record News |periodical=[[NME|NME]] |publisher=[[IPC_Media|IPC Media]] |location=London, England |page=48 |date=17 October 1981}}</ref>。该专辑收录了乐队自1974年第一首进榜歌曲《{{lang|en|[[Seven_Seas_of_Rhye|Seven Seas of Rhye]]}}》到1980年热门歌曲《{{lang|en|[[Flash_(歌曲)|Flash]]}}》之间发行的销售额最高的单曲。它没有统一的曲目名单和封面，而是有不同的各国家地区版本，各自选取了在当地取得商业成功的歌。

该专辑发行后立即取得了成功，在[[英國專輯排行榜|英國專輯排行榜]]的第一名位置停留了四周。它继续在英国榜上停留了超过五百多周，卖出了六百万张，成为了[[英国最畅销专辑列表|英国历史上销量最高]]的专辑<ref name="uk-bestseller">[http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/entertainment/6151050.stm Queen head all-time sales chart] {{WebCite|url=https://www.webcitation.org/5mq6i4yv1?url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/entertainment/6151050.stm |date=20100117030949 |dateformat=iso }} [[BBC|BBC]] Retrieved 23 January 2011</ref><ref name=BPIC>{{cite web| url=http://www.bpi.co.uk/assets/files/top%2040%20albums.pdf| title=BPI Highest Retail Sales| publisher=[[British_Phonographic_Industry|British Phonographic Industry]]| accessdate=2011-01-17| archive-date=2016-03-03| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303191500/http://www.bpi.co.uk/assets/files/top%2040%20albums.pdf| dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>[http://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-354650/Queen-longest-reigning-chart-act.html Queen becomes longest reigning chart act] {{Wayback|url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-354650/Queen-longest-reigning-chart-act.html |date=20110920125221 }} ''[[Daily_Mail|Daily Mail]]'' Retrieved 23 January 2011</ref>。它在美国获得了[[RIAA认证|8×白金唱片认证]]。该专辑是皇后乐队在全球范围内商业上最成功的专辑，成为[[全球最畅销专辑列表|世界历史上最畅销的专辑之一]]<ref>[http://news.bbc.co.uk/hi/english/static/in_depth/entertainment/2002/jubilee/popup/5.stm In Pictures: 50 years of pop] {{WebCite|url=https://www.webcitation.org/69UgxyxZz?url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/hi/english/static/in_depth/entertainment/2002/jubilee/popup/5.stm |date=20120728122855 |dateformat=iso }} ''[[BBC_News|BBC News]]'' Retrieved 17 January 2011</ref><ref>[http://www.riaa.com/goldandplatinumdata.php?resultpage=2&table=SEARCH_RESULTS&action=&title=&artist=queen&format=&debutLP=&category=&sex=&releaseDate=&requestNo=&type=&level=&label=&company=&certificationDate=&awardDescription=&catalogNo=&aSex=&rec_id=&charField=&gold=&platinum=&multiPlat=&level2=&certDate=&album=&id=&after=&before=&startMonth=1&endMonth=1&startYear=1958&endYear=2010&sort=CertificationDate&perPage=50 RIAA - Gold and Platinum] {{Wayback|url=http://www.riaa.com/goldandplatinumdata.php?resultpage=2&table=SEARCH_RESULTS&action=&title=&artist=queen&format=&debutLP=&category=&sex=&releaseDate=&requestNo=&type=&level=&label=&company=&certificationDate=&awardDescription=&catalogNo=&aSex=&rec_id=&charField=&gold=&platinum=&multiPlat=&level2=&certDate=&album=&id=&after=&before=&startMonth=1&endMonth=1&startYear=1958&endYear=2010&sort=CertificationDate&perPage=50 |date=20150904041257 }} ''Recording Industry Association of America'' Retrieved 23 January 2011</ref>。

